            <title><![CDATA[【[哆啦A梦害怕]全部中招！#这4个习惯会导致牙龈萎缩#】专家表示，牙龈萎缩往往不是自然老化，而是由于生活中自己的不重视，或者是不懂得保护牙齿：①刷牙不到位...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦害怕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_03haipa-32e9b53caf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>全部中招！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%994%E4%B8%AA%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%89%99%E9%BE%88%E8%90%8E%E7%BC%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%994%E4%B8%AA%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%89%99%E9%BE%88%E8%90%8E%E7%BC%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这4个习惯会导致牙龈萎缩#</span></a>】专家表示，牙龈萎缩往往不是自然老化，而是由于生活中自己的不重视，或者是不懂得保护牙齿：①刷牙不到位；②刷牙用力过猛；③经常吃硬物；④经常吃过酸性食物👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5006925260324888" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1gy1hnaujci9mwj20u01hcn39.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5KRiUg8rlx08cVEAYvsQ01041200bbRv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709385616&amp;ssig=O9LBh6Fbz1&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/FQG7xE4qlx08cVEATePC010412006j9B0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709385616&amp;ssig=PJTCkl4Ipj&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/QRkWhoIMlx08cVEAZjyU010412003sy50E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709385616&amp;ssig=JdelVJqHrm&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5006925260324888" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
