        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【#三类疾病容易导致肥胖#[并不简单]】#怎样判断自己是不是肥胖#？医学上一般使用体重指数进行衡量，是基于身高和体重而计算出的指标（BMI）。BMI=体重（千克）/...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三类疾病容易导致肥胖#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#怎样判断自己是不是肥胖#</span></a>？医学上一般使用体重指数进行衡量，是基于身高和体重而计算出的指标（BMI）。BMI=体重（千克）/【身高（米）的平方】，超过24是超重，超过28就认为是肥胖。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>专家提醒，体重超标的患者，可能不是单纯性肥胖，内分泌疾病、甲状腺功能减退、肾上腺疾病都可能导致肥胖👇🏻 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%BA%A6%E5%85%AB%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9C%89%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%E7%97%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%BA%A6%E5%85%AB%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9C%89%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%E7%97%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#全球约八分之一人口有肥胖症#</span></a> （央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YoE5n5" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
